sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant O as Orchestrator session
    participant V as Verifier (subagent)
    participant D as scripts/dispatch-reworks
    participant B as claude --bg sessions
    participant T as External terminals
    participant M as claude agents (fresh pane)

    V->>O: emits REWORK_MANIFEST.md
    O->>O: EnterWorktree creates N rework worktrees
    O-->>U: prints dispatch instruction

    alt --bg (default, headless)
        U->>D: scripts/dispatch-reworks
        D->>B: claude --bg /resume-rework (N times)
        Note right of B: marker per session at ~/.claude/rework_sessions/SHORT_ID
        D-->>U: N session IDs and claude logs hints
        U->>M: open fresh Cursor pane, run claude agents
        M-->>U: unified live state of N reworks
        B-->>U: macOS notification on Stop (osascript hook)
    else --terminals (visible)
        U->>D: scripts/dispatch-reworks --terminals
        D->>T: open claude-cli:// links (N times)
        T-->>U: terminal windows with /resume-rework pre-filled
        U->>T: press Enter in each window
    end

    B->>O: reworks complete, merge back and re-verify
